=Description=

"To learn more about  'Artificial Intelligence and the Future of Power', visit  https://www.aiandpower.com/​​

The discussion focuses on Chapters 4 & 5 of the AI book. Computer Science is taking over R&D in genomes. How is AI related to intellectual property theft in agriculture, traditional medicines, and plants? Dr. Vandana Shiva is world famous as a champion of India’s rights of plant-based intellectual property, traditional agriculture, etc. against global giants. This is a vibrant discussion that ought to wake up leaders of farmers’ rights, animal rights, science, privacy and data laws, globalization, decolonization, etc."

